if you wish to reproduce this project the falowing hardware list may be of assistance.

board: Raspberry Pi Zero 2w
thermocouple amp: MAX 31855
roaster: popper gen 2
dac: MCP4728


Popper coffee roaster

Grey 2025 / 3rd production-run Popper
7 numbered stepped heat levels
Improved fan motor
Built-in 7 minute roast + 3 minute cooldown cycle


Raspberry Pi Zero 2w
Hostname: RoastPi
Runs the control service
Creates the PopperRoaster Wi-Fi network


MAX31855 thermocouple amplifier

Reads bean temperature
Uses SPI
SPI device: /dev/spidev0.0
Code uses SPI bus 0, device 0
Speed: 5,000,000 Hz


MCP4728 DAC

I2C address: 0x60
I2C bus: 1
Reference voltage: 5.0 V
DAC Channel B / channel 1: heat output


5v power suply for Raspberry Pi
